WEBVTT

00:34.240 --> 00:35.760
<font color="white">Ah, good morning Mrs H.</font>

00:37.080 --> 00:39.520
<font color="yellow">Isn't it custom to get</font>
<font color="yellow">dressed in the morning?</font>

00:39.520 --> 00:41.720
<font color="white">I shall be retiring to my room.</font>

00:49.760 --> 00:50.800
<font color="cyan">Mrs Hall?</font>

00:54.120 --> 00:55.400
<font color="lime">Triss? </font><font color="white">Shh!</font>

00:55.400 --> 00:57.320
<font color="cyan">Can't get the thing through</font>
<font color="cyan">the...</font>

00:57.320 --> 00:58.360
<font color="yellow">Come here...</font>

00:59.480 --> 01:01.680
<font color="cyan">Bloody cufflinks.</font>
<font color="yellow">Oh, come into the light.</font>

01:02.960 --> 01:04.760
<font color="lime">Morning Siegfried.</font>
<font color="cyan">Morning.</font>

01:04.760 --> 01:05.880
<font color="lime">New suit?</font>

01:05.880 --> 01:07.320
<font color="cyan">What? Oh, yes.</font>

01:07.320 --> 01:09.880
<font color="cyan">I'm being put through my paces</font>
<font color="cyan">at Darrowby Racecourse.</font>

01:09.880 --> 01:12.240
<font color="cyan">The attending vet's retiring.</font>

01:12.240 --> 01:14.480
<font color="yellow">It'll be quite the honour</font>
<font color="yellow">if he gets the role.</font>

01:15.760 --> 01:17.200
<font color="cyan">It's no bloody good.</font>

01:17.200 --> 01:19.680
<font color="cyan">There's another pair in my office.</font>

01:19.680 --> 01:22.680
<font color="yellow">He's wanted the job some time,</font>
<font color="yellow">it's made him a little emotional.</font>

01:29.800 --> 01:33.760
<font color="cyan">Now, James, I'm hoping to be</font>
<font color="cyan">back for afternoon rounds,</font>

01:33.760 --> 01:36.240
<font color="cyan">but I need you to hold</font>
<font color="cyan">the fort till then.</font>

01:36.240 --> 01:38.080
<font color="lime">Of course.</font>

01:38.080 --> 01:40.120
<font color="lime">Thank you! I won't let you down.</font>

01:40.120 --> 01:42.960
<font color="cyan">Ah, many have said the same</font>
<font color="cyan">but few rise to...</font>

01:44.440 --> 01:46.080
<font color="cyan">We've been robbed!</font>

01:49.160 --> 01:50.440
<font color="cyan">This was full only last week.</font>

01:53.120 --> 01:54.160
<font color="cyan">What you doing?</font>

01:54.160 --> 01:55.280
<font color="white">I was, just...</font>

01:55.280 --> 01:58.200
<font color="cyan">Why aren't you dressed?</font>
<font color="cyan">It's nearly nine o'clock.</font>

01:58.200 --> 01:59.480
<font color="cyan">Come and explain yourself.</font>

02:01.520 --> 02:03.400
<font color="cyan">Is that your doing?</font>

02:03.400 --> 02:04.520
<font color="white">I haven't touched it.</font>

02:04.520 --> 02:07.600
<font color="yellow">I took the last of the petty</font>
<font color="yellow">cash for this week's shop.</font>

02:07.600 --> 02:09.280
<font color="cyan">How is it possible?</font>

02:09.280 --> 02:11.640
<font color="cyan">We've worked harder than ever</font>
<font color="cyan">since James arrived.</font>

02:11.640 --> 02:14.200
<font color="cyan">More surgery time. Where's all</font>
<font color="cyan">the money from all that gone?</font>

02:14.200 --> 02:15.440
<font color="lime">Shall I call the police?</font>

02:16.680 --> 02:19.400
<font color="yellow">Still in the farmer's pockets,</font>
<font color="yellow">I should imagine.</font>

02:19.400 --> 02:21.360
<font color="yellow">When was the last time you</font>
<font color="yellow">chased the bills?</font>

02:22.480 --> 02:24.080
<font color="cyan">You. </font><font color="white">Me?</font>

02:27.440 --> 02:28.560
<font color="cyan">It's market day.</font>

02:29.960 --> 02:32.160
<font color="yellow">Time to earn your keep</font>
<font color="yellow">like the rest of us.</font>

02:33.000 --> 02:34.040
<font color="lime">Good luck today.</font>

02:40.120 --> 02:41.160
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

02:45.120 --> 02:46.160
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

02:47.760 --> 02:49.760
<font color="yellow">I'll keep an eye on Tristan for you.</font>

02:49.760 --> 02:51.400
<font color="cyan">Yes, do.</font>

02:51.400 --> 02:52.440
<font color="cyan">Remember.</font>

02:52.440 --> 02:54.040
<font color="cyan">Spare the rod. Spoil the child.</font>

03:13.600 --> 03:14.840
<font color="lime">You'll have to go back.</font>

03:16.200 --> 03:18.080
<font color="lime">Go back! </font><font color="yellow">Oh, OK.</font>

03:18.080 --> 03:19.440
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>
<font color="yellow">Much obliged.</font>

03:20.960 --> 03:22.520
<font color="lime">Put it in reverse and...</font>

03:23.960 --> 03:25.160
<font color="lime">Oh, for Pete's sake.</font>

03:34.560 --> 03:35.600
<font color="lime">Well, what...</font>

03:46.080 --> 03:47.760
<font color="yellow">I thought I was going back?</font>

03:47.760 --> 03:49.400
<font color="lime">I thought so too but...</font>

03:49.400 --> 03:51.000
<font color="lime">Never mind.</font>

03:51.000 --> 03:52.040
<font color="yellow">Well, hold on.</font>

04:10.400 --> 04:13.600
<font color="yellow">You're Siegfried's chap,</font>
<font color="yellow">aren't you? Harris!</font>

04:13.600 --> 04:15.160
<font color="lime">Herriot. </font><font color="yellow">Ah, that's it.</font>

04:15.160 --> 04:17.360
<font color="yellow">Yes, I do apologise.</font>

04:17.360 --> 04:19.200
<font color="yellow">Have a good day.</font>

04:19.200 --> 04:20.240
<font color="lime">You too.</font>

04:55.040 --> 04:56.080
<font color="white">Farnon.</font>

04:59.360 --> 05:00.400
<font color="cyan">General Ransom.</font>

05:06.080 --> 05:08.480
<font color="cyan">Hello, I didn't</font>
<font color="cyan">expecting to see you today.</font>

05:08.480 --> 05:10.200
<font color="cyan">I thought you'd be with Andante.</font>

05:10.200 --> 05:12.760
<font color="yellow">Soames is bringing him down later.</font>
<font color="cyan">How's he looking for tomorrow?</font>

05:12.760 --> 05:14.480
<font color="yellow">Well, I err, I'd put a fiver on him.</font>

05:15.440 --> 05:17.680
<font color="white">Which other breeders do you</font>
<font color="white">work with, Farnon?</font>

05:17.680 --> 05:20.960
<font color="cyan">Well, virtually all my clients have</font>
<font color="cyan">horses that need attending to.</font>

05:20.960 --> 05:22.600
<font color="white">Racehorses?</font>

05:22.600 --> 05:24.320
<font color="cyan">Well, just Hugh, really.</font>

05:25.880 --> 05:29.760
<font color="white">We were hoping for someone with</font>
<font color="white">a pertinent experience.</font>

05:29.760 --> 05:32.520
<font color="white">There's quite a bit of difference</font>
<font color="white">between a cart horse</font>

05:32.520 --> 05:33.840
<font color="white">and a thoroughbred.</font>

05:33.840 --> 05:35.200
<font color="cyan">Not anatomically speaking.</font>

05:35.200 --> 05:36.880
<font color="cyan">A horse is always a horse...</font>

05:36.880 --> 05:38.920
<font color="yellow">My father wouldn't have</font>
<font color="yellow">had any other vet</font>

05:38.920 --> 05:40.600
<font color="yellow">but Siegfried in his stables.</font>

05:40.600 --> 05:42.240
<font color="cyan">A good man.</font>
<font color="cyan">Loved his horses.</font>

05:46.680 --> 05:48.480
<font color="yellow">There's a horse down.</font>

05:48.480 --> 05:50.520
<font color="white">Time to show us</font>
<font color="white">what you're made of Farnon.</font>

05:55.520 --> 05:56.760
<font color="lime">Mrs Calvert?</font>

05:56.760 --> 05:58.200
<font color="white">Hello, hello, hello.</font>

05:58.200 --> 06:01.280
<font color="white">What's this? We've got</font>
<font color="white">the new chap, today?</font>

06:03.240 --> 06:05.440
<font color="lime">I've been at the practise for a</font>
<font color="lime">while, actually.</font>

06:05.440 --> 06:10.280
<font color="white">Oh, ain't he got a nice smile.</font>

06:10.280 --> 06:12.800
<font color="white">He's a real happy Harry, this one.</font>

06:26.320 --> 06:27.480
<font color="lime">106.</font>

06:27.560 --> 06:29.160
<font color="white">That don't sound too clever.</font>

06:35.560 --> 06:37.080
<font color="lime">Going like the clappers.</font>

06:40.200 --> 06:42.080
<font color="lime">What's she been doing</font>
<font color="lime">these last few days?</font>

06:42.080 --> 06:45.880
<font color="white">She was out in the field,</font>
<font color="white">chasing round after the dog.</font>

06:45.880 --> 06:48.320
<font color="white">It were roasting yesterday.</font>

06:48.320 --> 06:49.880
<font color="lime">Well, there's your problem.</font>

06:49.880 --> 06:50.920
<font color="white">Hmm?</font>

06:50.920 --> 06:52.400
<font color="lime">She's got heat exhaustion.</font>

06:52.400 --> 06:53.800
<font color="white">Well, what's to be done?</font>

06:53.800 --> 06:55.600
<font color="lime">Let's start with a couple</font>
<font color="lime">buckets of water.</font>

06:57.040 --> 06:58.080
<font color="lime">Quick as you like.</font>

07:03.960 --> 07:05.080
<font color="cyan">Would you mind, Hugh?</font>

07:09.720 --> 07:11.480
<font color="cyan">What's up with you, fella?</font>

07:13.000 --> 07:14.840
<font color="cyan">Done yourself a mischief, have you?</font>

07:16.840 --> 07:18.480
<font color="cyan">Keep back, please.</font>
<font color="cyan">Give me room.</font>

07:26.520 --> 07:28.560
<font color="cyan">No sign of sprain or fracture.</font>

07:28.560 --> 07:30.160
<font color="white">Then why is he not getting up?</font>

07:42.760 --> 07:44.720
<font color="cyan">There it is.</font>
<font color="cyan">There's no nystagmus.</font>

07:44.720 --> 07:47.200
<font color="cyan">But that doesn't mean he didn't</font>
<font color="cyan">hit his head on the way down.</font>

07:47.200 --> 07:50.040
<font color="cyan">What we need is to get him</font>
<font color="cyan">up and walking.</font>

07:50.040 --> 07:51.080
<font color="cyan">Sooner the better.</font>

07:52.320 --> 07:53.960
<font color="cyan">Gentlemen, I'll need your help.</font>

07:56.480 --> 07:57.720
<font color="cyan">Come on, boy.</font>

07:57.720 --> 07:59.000
<font color="cyan">Up we go.</font>

07:59.000 --> 08:00.960
<font color="cyan">Come on, boy.</font>
<font color="cyan">Come on.</font>

08:00.960 --> 08:03.120
<font color="cyan">Up we go. Come on.</font>

08:04.120 --> 08:05.640
<font color="lime">He's not having it, Siegfried.</font>

08:05.640 --> 08:07.280
<font color="cyan">Right.</font>

08:07.280 --> 08:10.160
<font color="cyan">I think he's probably still</font>
<font color="cyan">winded from the fall.</font>

08:10.160 --> 08:14.160
<font color="cyan">Let's just, um,</font>
<font color="cyan">let's just take a moment.</font>

08:14.160 --> 08:15.680
<font color="white">Shouldn't you be doing something?</font>

08:15.680 --> 08:17.400
<font color="cyan">Nature takes the time she needs.</font>

08:17.400 --> 08:18.440
<font color="white">God.</font>

08:18.440 --> 08:20.800
<font color="white">Bring the tractor, we're going to</font>
<font color="white">have to winch him off.</font>

08:20.800 --> 08:22.760
<font color="cyan">I can't let you to do that.</font>
<font color="white">Excuse me?</font>

08:22.760 --> 08:24.560
<font color="cyan">Nobody is winching this horse</font>
<font color="cyan">anywhere.</font>

08:24.560 --> 08:25.960
<font color="cyan">It's cruel and unnecessary.</font>

08:30.640 --> 08:34.039
<font color="cyan">Yes, you've given yourself a fright,</font>
<font color="cyan">haven't you? But you're fine.</font>

08:35.400 --> 08:36.880
<font color="cyan">Get some more air in to your lungs.</font>

08:38.200 --> 08:39.480
<font color="cyan">Happy to have another go?</font>

08:46.040 --> 08:47.280
<font color="cyan">Come on then.</font>

08:47.280 --> 08:48.760
<font color="cyan">Up and at 'em.</font>

08:48.760 --> 08:50.440
<font color="cyan">That's the one.</font>

08:50.440 --> 08:52.160
<font color="cyan">Let's be having you, there we are.</font>

08:53.560 --> 08:54.920
<font color="cyan">Well done.</font>

08:54.920 --> 08:55.960
<font color="cyan">Walk on.</font>

09:01.280 --> 09:04.040
<font color="white">I'm not used to being spoken</font>
<font color="white">to in that manner.</font>

09:04.040 --> 09:07.040
<font color="cyan">And I'm not used to putting personal</font>
<font color="cyan">niceties before good</font>

09:07.040 --> 09:09.200
<font color="cyan">professional practice, sir.</font>

09:30.279 --> 09:32.559
<font color="white">A shilling and two pence, please.</font>

09:32.559 --> 09:33.599
<font color="yellow">Good boy.</font>

09:37.039 --> 09:38.079
<font color="yellow">Keep it up.</font>

09:40.039 --> 09:41.759
<font color="white">Ah, Mr Dinsdale -</font>
<font color="white">how fortuitous!</font>

09:43.279 --> 09:46.359
<font color="white">Erm, oh, my you have let it build</font>
<font color="white">up, one pound and threepence.</font>

09:46.799 --> 09:48.799
<font color="lime">Oh, I don't have any on me now.</font>

09:49.839 --> 09:51.279
<font color="white">And yet here you are.</font>

09:51.279 --> 09:52.359
<font color="lime">Buying things.</font>

09:52.359 --> 09:54.079
<font color="white">With money one would presume?</font>

09:54.079 --> 09:57.199
<font color="lime">Well, mother gives me</font>
<font color="lime">money for vegetables.</font>

09:57.199 --> 09:58.839
<font color="lime">Not a penny more not a penny less.</font>

10:00.959 --> 10:02.199
<font color="cyan">If it's threepence a hen,</font>

10:02.199 --> 10:05.799
<font color="cyan">how about I put a shilling in your</font>
<font color="cyan">pocket and take six off your hands?</font>

10:05.799 --> 10:07.999
<font color="lime">Jenny what do you think you're</font>
<font color="lime">playing at?</font>

10:07.999 --> 10:09.039
<font color="cyan">Buying hens!</font>

10:09.039 --> 10:10.399
<font color="lime">Sorry.</font>

10:10.399 --> 10:13.159
<font color="white">Ah, the delightful Miss Alderson.</font>

10:13.159 --> 10:14.399
<font color="lime">Yes, Triss, what, is it?</font>

10:15.959 --> 10:18.119
<font color="white">Um, nothing it can wait.</font>

10:19.759 --> 10:22.039
<font color="cyan">But them were good hens.</font>
<font color="cyan">Old man Cocker says so.</font>

10:22.039 --> 10:24.079
<font color="lime">Oh, if old man Cocker says so.</font>
<font color="lime">They must be.</font>

10:24.079 --> 10:26.039
<font color="cyan">You don't trust me to do anything.</font>

10:27.999 --> 10:29.039
<font color="yellow">I've been there.</font>

10:30.039 --> 10:32.639
<font color="yellow">The shouting, the tantrums.</font>

10:33.839 --> 10:35.119
<font color="lime">Your Edward was the same?</font>

10:36.119 --> 10:38.719
<font color="yellow">He was but I were thinking more</font>
<font color="yellow">of...</font>

10:40.119 --> 10:41.159
<font color="lime">Mr Farnon?</font>

10:41.879 --> 10:43.239
<font color="yellow">Never mind.</font>

10:43.239 --> 10:46.199
<font color="lime">I just want her to know there's more</font>
<font color="lime">to life than being a farmer.</font>

10:46.199 --> 10:47.839
<font color="lime">How you have no time to yourself.</font>

10:50.559 --> 10:52.479
<font color="yellow">Want me to take her for the day?</font>

10:53.559 --> 10:54.719
<font color="lime">It wouldn't put you out?</font>

10:55.719 --> 10:57.079
<font color="yellow">Not a bit of it.</font>

10:57.079 --> 10:58.199
<font color="yellow">Have a break.</font>

10:58.199 --> 10:59.239
<font color="yellow">You deserve it.</font>

11:11.239 --> 11:12.319
<font color="white">Cheeky beggar.</font>

11:18.519 --> 11:20.239
<font color="lime">Pint of best when you're ready,</font>
<font color="lime">Maggie.</font>

11:20.239 --> 11:21.279
<font color="yellow">Coming right up.</font>

11:23.119 --> 11:24.159
<font color="white">Ah, Mr Dinsdale.</font>

11:24.599 --> 11:26.279
<font color="white">That's a healthy wedge you</font>
<font color="white">have there.</font>

11:27.519 --> 11:28.879
<font color="lime">More flush than I thought.</font>

11:28.879 --> 11:29.999
<font color="white">So it seems.</font>

11:29.999 --> 11:32.199
<font color="white">Don't expect him to buy a round</font>
<font color="white">though chaps,</font>

11:32.199 --> 11:34.159
<font color="white">not without the say</font>
<font color="white">so of his good lady wife, eh?</font>

11:43.159 --> 11:46.599
<font color="yellow">If you're doing business in here,</font>
<font color="yellow">least you can do is buy a drink.</font>

11:46.599 --> 11:49.039
<font color="white">Hello, you're new.</font>

11:49.039 --> 11:50.559
<font color="yellow">What'll it be?</font>

11:50.559 --> 11:51.759
<font color="white">I shouldn't really.</font>

11:54.079 --> 11:57.719
<font color="yellow">Drink leads to loose tongues</font>
<font color="yellow">and even looser wallets.</font>

11:58.919 --> 12:01.759
<font color="yellow">You want people to part with their</font>
<font color="yellow">money, this is no bad place for it.</font>

12:05.519 --> 12:07.839
<font color="yellow">But you got to buy a drink first.</font>

12:10.839 --> 12:12.519
<font color="cyan">Did you write all these recipes?</font>

12:13.719 --> 12:14.919
<font color="yellow">And my mother.</font>

12:16.519 --> 12:18.079
<font color="yellow">And her mother before her.</font>

12:19.479 --> 12:21.759
<font color="yellow">All our family secrets.</font>

12:21.759 --> 12:23.959
<font color="cyan">My sister does</font>
<font color="cyan">most of the baking at home.</font>

12:23.959 --> 12:26.479
<font color="yellow">That's because it's her job</font>
<font color="yellow">to look after you.</font>

12:26.479 --> 12:28.239
<font color="cyan">I don't need looking after.</font>

12:29.719 --> 12:32.119
<font color="cyan">We were born to the land</font>
<font color="cyan">to work the land.</font>

12:35.999 --> 12:38.239
<font color="yellow">Is that something you've</font>
<font color="yellow">heard your dad say?</font>

12:40.679 --> 12:42.839
<font color="white">PHONE RINGING</font>

12:49.039 --> 12:51.639
<font color="yellow">Hugh Hulton's estate, right.</font>

12:52.759 --> 12:55.159
<font color="yellow">I'll get someone</font>
<font color="yellow">up to you as quick as I can.</font>

12:55.159 --> 12:56.559
<font color="yellow">Bye...</font>
<font color="white">THEY HANG UP</font>

12:58.839 --> 13:01.919
<font color="cyan">And how did you know what was wrong?</font>
<font color="cyan">Were you guessing?</font>

13:01.919 --> 13:03.359
<font color="lime">Oh, no, we're professional vets.</font>

13:03.359 --> 13:04.599
<font color="lime">We never guess.</font>

13:04.599 --> 13:08.519
<font color="lime">First I took her heart rate,</font>
<font color="lime">and then I checked her temperature.</font>

13:08.519 --> 13:11.679
<font color="lime">That along with the clinical history</font>
<font color="lime">meant there was only one</font>

13:11.679 --> 13:13.319
<font color="lime">possible diagnosis.</font>

13:13.319 --> 13:14.959
<font color="yellow">He's a clever clogs, isn't he?</font>

13:14.959 --> 13:17.159
<font color="cyan">James has been seeing to</font>
<font color="cyan">a sunburnt calf.</font>

13:17.159 --> 13:18.879
<font color="lime">Heat exhaustion.</font>

13:18.879 --> 13:20.799
<font color="yellow">We just had</font>
<font color="yellow">a call from Hulton Manor.</font>

13:20.799 --> 13:22.199
<font color="yellow">Horse with colic.</font>

13:22.199 --> 13:23.599
<font color="cyan">That's Hugh's house.</font>

13:23.599 --> 13:25.079
<font color="cyan">Can I go with him, Auntie Audrey?</font>

13:25.079 --> 13:28.399
<font color="yellow">No your sister will be back soon,</font>
<font color="yellow">she'll wonder where you got to.</font>

13:28.399 --> 13:29.559
<font color="lime">Maybe next time.</font>

13:29.559 --> 13:30.599
<font color="cyan">Uh.</font>

13:32.999 --> 13:34.759
<font color="yellow">How about we finish off them faces?</font>

13:35.799 --> 13:39.319
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear,</font>
<font color="yellow">he's a one grumpy one isn't he?</font>

13:39.319 --> 13:40.359
<font color="cyan">It's our Helen.</font>

13:44.239 --> 13:46.799
<font color="cyan">So young Farnon here says,</font>
<font color="cyan">'Where'd you want a six,</font>

13:46.799 --> 13:47.959
<font color="cyan">in the bloody bus depot?'</font>

13:47.959 --> 13:50.279
<font color="white">LAUGHTER</font>

13:50.279 --> 13:51.679
<font color="cyan">You're a good lad.</font>

13:51.679 --> 13:54.159
<font color="white">Oh, yes, honestly, Mr Lunn,</font>
<font color="white">that's why it pains me</font>

13:55.119 --> 13:57.479
<font color="white">so to turn to matters more serious.</font>

13:59.999 --> 14:01.399
<font color="cyan">Don't you worry.</font>

14:01.399 --> 14:03.319
<font color="cyan">You tell me how much it is?</font>

14:03.319 --> 14:04.359
<font color="lime">Here, Mags.</font>

14:05.519 --> 14:07.839
<font color="lime">Darrowby Classic,</font>
<font color="lime">12:30 tomorrow.</font>

14:07.839 --> 14:08.879
<font color="lime">Andante to win.</font>

14:23.239 --> 14:25.479
<font color="white">You're a dark horse,</font>
<font color="white">aren't you?</font>

14:25.479 --> 14:27.399
<font color="yellow">Birds of a feather.</font>

14:27.399 --> 14:28.919
<font color="yellow">You staying for another?</font>

14:28.919 --> 14:30.199
<font color="white">Don't mind if I do.</font>

14:30.199 --> 14:31.599
<font color="cyan">Is he paying for a drink?</font>

14:31.599 --> 14:36.839
<font color="lime">Lads, Tristan Farnon he's buying</font>
<font color="lime">himself his own pint!</font>

14:36.839 --> 14:38.399
<font color="lime">It's a miracle.</font>

14:38.399 --> 14:40.199
<font color="white">Now, now I always pay my way.</font>

14:40.199 --> 14:42.799
<font color="white">In fact, Henry, why don't</font>
<font color="white">I get you one.</font>

14:44.039 --> 14:45.759
<font color="lime">Well, that's dreadful decent of you.</font>

14:45.759 --> 14:47.919
<font color="white">How about one for everybody?</font>

14:47.919 --> 14:49.359
<font color="cyan">How every kind of you.</font>

15:06.519 --> 15:08.519
<font color="lime">Mr Soames? James Herriott...</font>

15:18.239 --> 15:19.319
<font color="white">HORSE NEIGHS LOUDLY</font>

15:19.319 --> 15:20.639
<font color="lime">How long's he been like this?</font>

15:20.639 --> 15:22.239
<font color="yellow">Since this morning.</font>

15:22.239 --> 15:24.839
<font color="yellow">Just give him a shot of arecoline,</font>
<font color="yellow">that'll sort him.</font>

15:30.039 --> 15:31.959
<font color="white">HORSE NEIGHS LOUDLY</font>

15:31.959 --> 15:33.199
<font color="lime">This is no ordinary colic.</font>

15:33.199 --> 15:35.039
<font color="yellow">What the hell is it then?</font>

15:35.039 --> 15:37.959
<font color="lime">I won't know for sure</font>
<font color="lime">until I've given him an examination.</font>

15:37.959 --> 15:41.119
<font color="yellow">I've been running stables here</font>
<font color="yellow">since you were in short trousers.</font>

15:41.119 --> 15:44.319
<font color="yellow">I know what colic looks like.</font>

15:44.319 --> 15:48.159
<font color="lime">Look, he's due at the racecourse to</font>
<font color="lime">settle in for tomorrow.</font>

15:52.399 --> 15:54.399
<font color="lime">I'll need soap and water.</font>
<font color="yellow">What the devil for?</font>

15:54.399 --> 15:56.239
<font color="yellow">You've done nowt</font>
<font color="yellow">and now you want a wash?</font>

15:56.239 --> 15:58.559
<font color="lime">Get a head collar on</font>
<font color="lime">so I can examine him.</font>

15:58.559 --> 15:59.599
<font color="lime">Now, please.</font>

16:06.119 --> 16:08.279
<font color="lime">Steady, boy. I know.</font>

16:08.279 --> 16:09.279
<font color="lime">I know.</font>

16:20.919 --> 16:22.679
<font color="lime">Oh, you poor thing.</font>

16:33.159 --> 16:34.839
<font color="yellow">Well, then? Spit it out.</font>

16:34.839 --> 16:36.199
<font color="lime">It's no ordinary colic.</font>

16:37.439 --> 16:38.839
<font color="yellow">What is it then?</font>

16:38.839 --> 16:42.239
<font color="lime">I'm really sorry to say it's a</font>
<font color="lime">torsion of the bowel, Mr Soames.</font>

16:42.239 --> 16:43.279
<font color="yellow">He's got a torsion?</font>

16:44.879 --> 16:46.319
<font color="yellow">What're you gonna do about it?</font>

16:47.959 --> 16:49.439
<font color="lime">Well, the bowel's twisted</font>

16:49.439 --> 16:51.959
<font color="lime">so badly that the circulation's been</font>
<font color="lime">cut off for some time.</font>

16:54.799 --> 16:56.159
<font color="lime">The tissue's died.</font>

16:56.159 --> 16:58.399
<font color="lime">Toxins are already building</font>
<font color="lime">up in the blood.</font>

16:59.479 --> 17:01.639
<font color="lime">There's nothing more that we can do.</font>

17:01.639 --> 17:03.079
<font color="lime">I'm sorry but it's already too late.</font>

17:04.199 --> 17:05.239
<font color="yellow">Too late for what?</font>

17:08.799 --> 17:09.999
<font color="lime">This horse will die.</font>

17:12.239 --> 17:14.559
<font color="lime">The only thing we can do is</font>
<font color="lime">end his life as quickly</font>

17:14.559 --> 17:16.398
<font color="lime">and painlessly as possible.</font>
<font color="yellow">Put him down?</font>

17:17.759 --> 17:19.959
<font color="yellow">Do you have you any idea how much</font>
<font color="yellow">this horse is worth?</font>

17:19.959 --> 17:21.878
<font color="lime">It doesn't make the blindest</font>
<font color="lime">bit of difference.</font>

17:21.878 --> 17:24.799
<font color="lime">He's in agony,</font>
<font color="lime">the sooner we proceed the better.</font>

17:24.799 --> 17:26.039
<font color="yellow">I want a second opinion.</font>

17:27.439 --> 17:29.839
<font color="yellow">I want Siegfried Farnon up here.</font>

17:29.839 --> 17:31.079
<font color="yellow">Mr Hulton swears by him.</font>

17:32.479 --> 17:36.319
<font color="yellow">Now come on lad, you don't</font>
<font color="yellow">want this on your shoulders.</font>

17:39.879 --> 17:42.079
<font color="cyan">Born to jump. Show him a fence and</font>
<font color="cyan">he'd have a go.</font>

17:44.199 --> 17:46.959
<font color="cyan">I went up one morning,</font>
<font color="cyan">and he'd dragged his feeding</font>

17:46.959 --> 17:50.199
<font color="cyan">trough into the middle of the</font>
<font color="cyan">paddock just so he could jump it.</font>

17:50.199 --> 17:51.799
<font color="cyan">Happy as Larry, he was.</font>

17:53.839 --> 17:54.919
<font color="white">WHISPERING</font>

17:57.759 --> 17:59.759
<font color="yellow">I'm afraid you'll have to excuse me,</font>
<font color="yellow">gentlemen.</font>

17:59.759 --> 18:02.119
<font color="yellow">Andante should've arrived by now.</font>
<font color="white">Of course.</font>

18:02.119 --> 18:03.159
<font color="yellow">General.</font>

18:05.039 --> 18:06.439
<font color="white">Could be a big day for Hulton</font>

18:06.439 --> 18:08.799
<font color="white">if that horse of his lives</font>
<font color="white">up to his promise.</font>

18:08.799 --> 18:11.559
<font color="cyan">It would be good to have a</font>
<font color="cyan">winner from a local stable.</font>

18:11.559 --> 18:13.599
<font color="cyan">A particular source of pride for me</font>
<font color="cyan">personally.</font>

18:13.599 --> 18:14.639
<font color="white">Why's that?</font>

18:14.639 --> 18:17.239
<font color="cyan">I've known Andante</font>
<font color="cyan">since he was a foal.</font>

18:17.239 --> 18:20.239
<font color="white">You're more of a farm vet</font>
<font color="white">aren't you?</font>

18:21.919 --> 18:23.319
<font color="cyan">I've built a strong practice.</font>

18:23.319 --> 18:24.599
<font color="white">Is that so?</font>

18:24.599 --> 18:26.639
<font color="cyan">I've taken on an excellent</font>
<font color="cyan">young vet.</font>

18:26.639 --> 18:28.599
<font color="cyan">And my brother's about to qualify.</font>

18:28.599 --> 18:29.639
<font color="cyan">I hope.</font>

18:30.959 --> 18:33.199
<font color="cyan">But horses have always</font>
<font color="cyan">been my passion.</font>

18:33.199 --> 18:34.239
<font color="white">Really?</font>

18:35.799 --> 18:37.959
<font color="cyan">Belgium, 1917.</font>

18:37.959 --> 18:39.119
<font color="cyan">Army Veterinary Corps.</font>

18:40.679 --> 18:42.399
<font color="white">Ypres?</font>
<font color="cyan">In the main.</font>

18:44.799 --> 18:46.439
<font color="cyan">The bravery of men who fought...</font>

18:47.759 --> 18:51.199
<font color="cyan">..matched only by the bravery of</font>
<font color="cyan">the horses that carried them there.</font>

18:52.999 --> 18:55.039
<font color="cyan">The things those poor souls endured.</font>

18:58.159 --> 18:59.639
<font color="cyan">And then we shot a lot of them.</font>

19:00.839 --> 19:02.879
<font color="cyan">Cheaper than bringing them</font>
<font color="cyan">home on boats you see.</font>

19:06.399 --> 19:08.159
<font color="cyan">If I can help a horse in pain...</font>

19:09.799 --> 19:12.239
<font color="cyan">..I feel in some way I'm repaying</font>
<font color="cyan">a debt of sorts.</font>

19:15.079 --> 19:16.359
<font color="cyan">There you have it.</font>

19:17.999 --> 19:20.199
<font color="white">We're trying out another</font>
<font color="white">fellow tomorrow.</font>

19:20.199 --> 19:22.199
<font color="cyan">I'm very grateful</font>
<font color="cyan">for the opportunity.</font>

19:25.079 --> 19:28.399
<font color="cyan">If I offended you earlier,</font>
<font color="cyan">it was only that...</font>

19:30.039 --> 19:31.759
<font color="cyan">..for me the animal always</font>
<font color="cyan">comes first.</font>

19:33.399 --> 19:34.879
<font color="cyan">Above all things.</font>

19:34.879 --> 19:35.919
<font color="white">As it should.</font>

19:38.799 --> 19:40.519
<font color="white">Come to the course tomorrow evening.</font>

19:40.519 --> 19:42.359
<font color="white">I hope to have some good</font>
<font color="white">news for you.</font>

19:52.319 --> 19:55.639
<font color="yellow">I've called, but Siegfried's</font>
<font color="yellow">already left the course.</font>

19:57.519 --> 19:58.959
<font color="lime">He's going mad with the pain of it.</font>

20:00.759 --> 20:02.759
<font color="lime">I can't let this go on.</font>
<font color="yellow">Oh, now just hold on...</font>

20:02.759 --> 20:05.639
<font color="lime">Maybe if you'd called me up sooner,</font>
<font color="lime">this might've been avoided.</font>

20:05.639 --> 20:07.519
<font color="lime">But not now.</font>

20:07.519 --> 20:09.759
<font color="lime">You might have failed in your duty</font>
<font color="lime">of care to that animal</font>

20:09.759 --> 20:11.439
<font color="lime">but there's no way I'm going to.</font>

20:26.759 --> 20:27.799
<font color="lime">What's his name?</font>

20:29.159 --> 20:30.439
<font color="yellow">Andante.</font>

20:57.159 --> 20:58.199
<font color="lime">Hold him tight.</font>

20:59.999 --> 21:01.159
<font color="lime">Steady, boy.</font>

21:03.559 --> 21:05.119
<font color="lime">Shhh.</font>

21:06.799 --> 21:07.999
<font color="lime">It's nearly over, Andante.</font>

21:19.399 --> 21:20.679
<font color="lime">Good lad.</font>

21:22.839 --> 21:23.879
<font color="lime">Good lad.</font>

21:25.479 --> 21:27.199
<font color="yellow">Mr Hulton.</font>
<font color="white">Why are you still here?</font>

21:36.079 --> 21:38.119
<font color="white">What do you mean? What's going on?</font>

21:38.119 --> 21:39.559
<font color="white">BANG</font>

21:39.559 --> 21:40.599
<font color="white">THUD</font>

21:45.639 --> 21:46.879
<font color="white">What have you just done?</font>

21:51.719 --> 21:53.759
<font color="white">What the hell have you just done!?</font>

21:53.759 --> 21:55.999
<font color="lime">Hugh! Listen to me!</font>
<font color="lime">He had a torsion.</font>

21:55.999 --> 21:59.279
<font color="lime">There was nothing else I could do</font>
<font color="lime">for him. He was in terrible pain.</font>

22:19.159 --> 22:20.399
<font color="white">Get out.</font>

22:21.759 --> 22:22.879
<font color="white">Now!</font>

23:10.279 --> 23:12.439
<font color="white">Ah, one of my employees.</font>

23:12.439 --> 23:13.479
<font color="white">James!</font>

23:15.159 --> 23:17.439
<font color="white">You look like you've lost</font>
<font color="white">a shilling and found a penny.</font>

23:21.319 --> 23:22.959
<font color="lime">I've just had to put a horse down.</font>

23:28.119 --> 23:29.879
<font color="lime">It was one of Hugh Hulton's horses.</font>

23:32.199 --> 23:33.399
<font color="lime">Andante.</font>

23:34.639 --> 23:35.679
<font color="white">Oh, good God.</font>

23:38.039 --> 23:39.959
<font color="white">I know what you need.</font>

23:39.959 --> 23:43.519
<font color="white">Maggie... Hold on a minute.</font>

23:44.839 --> 23:48.039
<font color="white">Maggie! Where's it all gone?</font>
<font color="white">This was full an hour ago.</font>

23:48.039 --> 23:49.559
<font color="yellow">Down their necks, I reckon.</font>

23:58.839 --> 24:01.439
<font color="white">Who's the second favourite</font>
<font color="white">in the Darrowby classic tomorrow?</font>

24:01.439 --> 24:02.479
<font color="yellow">Finlay Bay.</font>

24:02.479 --> 24:03.519
<font color="yellow">Ten to one.</font>

24:03.519 --> 24:06.279
<font color="yellow">But he's got no chance, I mean</font>
<font color="yellow">Andante gonna run away with it.</font>

24:08.759 --> 24:10.719
<font color="white">Put that on Finlay Bay to win.</font>

24:13.639 --> 24:16.559
<font color="cyan">I take great satisfaction in looking</font>
<font color="cyan">after our usual</font>

24:16.559 --> 24:18.919
<font color="cyan">clientele of cart horses</font>
<font color="cyan">and gymkhana ponies.</font>

24:18.919 --> 24:22.559
<font color="cyan">But to spend a day with those</font>
<font color="cyan">magnificent beasts,</font>

24:22.559 --> 24:23.599
<font color="cyan">bred to perfection.</font>

24:26.759 --> 24:28.119
<font color="cyan">And the General was impressed.</font>

24:29.799 --> 24:31.999
<font color="cyan">He had me down as an also-ran.</font>

24:31.999 --> 24:33.639
<font color="cyan">Now he knows I'm a thoroughbred.</font>

24:36.479 --> 24:38.359
<font color="yellow">I'm happy for you.</font>

24:38.359 --> 24:40.319
<font color="cyan">It's you I have to thank for it.</font>

24:40.319 --> 24:42.519
<font color="cyan">I don't think Ransom would have</font>
<font color="cyan">taken me as seriously</font>

24:42.519 --> 24:44.919
<font color="cyan">if I was still a one-man band.</font>

24:44.919 --> 24:46.679
<font color="cyan">You encouraged me to take on James.</font>

24:49.039 --> 24:51.399
<font color="yellow">I nudged you in the right direction.</font>

24:51.399 --> 24:53.639
<font color="cyan">Mrs Hall, you're considerably less</font>
<font color="cyan">braggadocios than</font>

24:53.639 --> 24:55.639
<font color="cyan">I would expect in the circumstances.</font>

24:55.639 --> 24:59.519
<font color="yellow">Oh, it's nothing,</font>
<font color="yellow">had Jenny Alderson for the day.</font>

25:00.839 --> 25:03.639
<font color="yellow">I thought I could help but I'm not</font>
<font color="yellow">sure I did her much good.</font>

25:03.639 --> 25:06.439
<font color="cyan">I never thought I'd see it. Mrs Hall</font>
<font color="cyan">waving the little white flag.</font>

25:06.439 --> 25:08.119
<font color="yellow">I'm not waving anything.</font>

25:08.119 --> 25:09.759
<font color="cyan">Undone by a 12--year-old child.</font>

25:10.919 --> 25:14.839
<font color="yellow">Well, it can't be easy having your</font>
<font color="yellow">big sister, acting like your mother.</font>

25:16.399 --> 25:18.599
<font color="cyan">It's no easier for the other party</font>
<font color="cyan">I assure you.</font>

25:19.639 --> 25:21.159
<font color="white">BANGING ON DOOR</font>

25:21.159 --> 25:22.239
<font color="cyan">No, you stay there.</font>

25:22.239 --> 25:23.279
<font color="cyan">I'll get this.</font>

25:27.199 --> 25:28.439
<font color="cyan">Hugh?</font>

25:28.439 --> 25:29.559
<font color="white">Has Herriot told you?</font>

25:32.039 --> 25:33.519
<font color="white">It is an outrage.</font>

25:33.519 --> 25:35.159
<font color="white">He had no right doing that</font>
<font color="white">to my horse.</font>

25:35.159 --> 25:36.399
<font color="cyan">I understand you're upset.</font>

25:36.399 --> 25:37.959
<font color="white">Oh, for God's sake,</font>
<font color="white">can you blame me?</font>

25:37.959 --> 25:39.839
<font color="cyan">It sounds like he was in terrible</font>
<font color="cyan">pain, Hugh.</font>

25:39.839 --> 25:42.239
<font color="cyan">I, I, I would have done</font>
<font color="cyan">the same thing. </font><font color="white">Would you?</font>

25:42.239 --> 25:43.759
<font color="cyan">With the same diagnosis? Yes.</font>

25:46.199 --> 25:48.399
<font color="cyan">We would never leave</font>
<font color="cyan">and animal in distress.</font>

25:48.399 --> 25:50.879
<font color="white">But that's just it. How do I know</font>
<font color="white">his diagnosis was right?</font>

25:50.879 --> 25:52.719
<font color="cyan">James is a very competent vet.</font>

25:52.719 --> 25:55.759
<font color="white">He's barely out of school!</font>
<font color="white">He should have got a second opinion.</font>

25:55.759 --> 25:57.279
<font color="white">He should have called for you.</font>

25:57.279 --> 26:00.359
<font color="white">You should have been there for him,</font>
<font color="white">Siegfried! </font><font color="cyan">Well, I wish I had been.</font>

26:17.119 --> 26:19.479
<font color="white">I've been advised to speak to</font>
<font color="white">a solicitor.</font>

26:19.479 --> 26:21.359
<font color="cyan">That's really not necessary.</font>

26:21.359 --> 26:22.839
<font color="white">He was a very valuable horse.</font>

26:23.799 --> 26:25.999
<font color="cyan">We can sort this</font>
<font color="cyan">out between ourselves, Hugh.</font>

26:25.999 --> 26:27.039
<font color="white">How?</font>

26:32.199 --> 26:34.399
<font color="cyan">I'll do a postmortem</font>
<font color="cyan">examination tomorrow.</font>

26:37.159 --> 26:38.519
<font color="white">And if Herriot made a mistake?</font>

26:38.519 --> 26:40.039
<font color="cyan">I'll deal with it.</font>

26:40.039 --> 26:41.359
<font color="cyan">You can be sure of that.</font>

26:46.559 --> 26:47.599
<font color="lime">Hugh I...</font>

26:48.519 --> 26:49.559
<font color="cyan">James come in.</font>

26:54.679 --> 26:55.719
<font color="cyan">Well?</font>

26:58.399 --> 27:00.599
<font color="lime">I couldn't let that poor</font>
<font color="lime">animal suffer.</font>

27:00.599 --> 27:02.999
<font color="cyan">And you're positive</font>
<font color="cyan">about your diagnosis?</font>

27:02.999 --> 27:04.039
<font color="lime">100%.</font>

27:07.999 --> 27:09.879
<font color="cyan">How are you fairing?</font>

27:09.879 --> 27:10.919
<font color="lime">Me? I'm...</font>

27:12.559 --> 27:13.999
<font color="lime">..all right.</font>

27:13.999 --> 27:15.039
<font color="lime">Trying to be.</font>

27:17.159 --> 27:18.479
<font color="lime">Shocked at first.</font>

27:20.919 --> 27:23.799
<font color="lime">It felt a terrible thing to do to</font>
<font color="lime">such a beautiful creature.</font>

27:25.919 --> 27:27.519
<font color="cyan">The first one is always the hardest.</font>

27:29.759 --> 27:32.479
<font color="cyan">I presume you did a full</font>
<font color="cyan">internal examination?</font>

27:32.479 --> 27:33.519
<font color="lime">Yes.</font>

27:33.519 --> 27:35.719
<font color="lime">I felt a tympanitic mass.</font>
<font color="lime">About halfway up the colon.</font>

27:35.719 --> 27:38.599
<font color="cyan">And it couldn't've been some other</font>
<font color="cyan">kind of blockage?</font>

27:38.599 --> 27:40.399
<font color="lime">No, I don't think so.</font>

27:40.399 --> 27:41.599
<font color="cyan">You don't think so?</font>

27:41.599 --> 27:43.479
<font color="lime">That's not what, it was a torsion.</font>

27:43.479 --> 27:45.279
<font color="cyan">A moment ago you said you were sure.</font>
<font color="lime">I am.</font>

27:46.399 --> 27:49.679
<font color="lime">I am sure. </font><font color="cyan">Because tomorrow there'll</font>
<font color="cyan">be nowhere to hide.</font>

27:49.679 --> 27:51.479
<font color="cyan">And if you're wrong,</font>

27:51.479 --> 27:53.679
<font color="cyan">I'm afraid,</font>
<font color="cyan">there will be consequences.</font>

28:03.679 --> 28:04.719
<font color="yellow">Breakfast's ready.</font>

28:06.719 --> 28:08.599
<font color="lime">I'm sorry, Mrs Hall.</font>

28:08.599 --> 28:09.639
<font color="lime">I'm not very hungry.</font>

28:10.879 --> 28:13.039
<font color="yellow">James won't be joining us.</font>

28:13.039 --> 28:15.279
<font color="cyan">I imagine he doesn't have the</font>
<font color="cyan">appetite for it.</font>

28:16.519 --> 28:17.999
<font color="yellow">What time's the postmortem?</font>

28:18.079 --> 28:19.119
<font color="cyan">Ten o'clock.</font>

28:20.159 --> 28:21.479
<font color="yellow">Get on with your list.</font>

28:21.479 --> 28:23.279
<font color="yellow">Let James get on with his.</font>

28:23.279 --> 28:25.679
<font color="yellow">There's nothing worrying</font>
<font color="yellow">will do for it.</font>

28:25.679 --> 28:27.079
<font color="white">Morning Siegfried.</font>

28:27.999 --> 28:29.039
<font color="cyan">Ledger. Now please.</font>

28:35.799 --> 28:37.119
<font color="cyan">You collected all this?</font>

28:37.119 --> 28:39.479
<font color="white">And I'm not done yet, far from it.</font>

28:39.479 --> 28:41.959
<font color="white">I wanna keep at it today.</font>
<font color="white">Finish the job off properly.</font>

28:41.959 --> 28:43.119
<font color="cyan">See that you do.</font>

28:43.119 --> 28:44.719
<font color="cyan">Money, now please.</font>

28:46.999 --> 28:50.879
<font color="white">Oh, I thought it would make more</font>
<font color="white">sense to give to you in one go.</font>

28:50.879 --> 28:53.079
<font color="white">Cleaner that way rather than</font>
<font color="white">piecemeal.</font>

28:53.079 --> 28:53.999
<font color="cyan">Money.</font>

28:59.519 --> 29:00.919
<font color="white">I left my wallet in my room.</font>

29:18.959 --> 29:20.319
<font color="white">DOOR CLOSES</font>

29:20.319 --> 29:22.839
<font color="cyan">Was that the front door?</font>
<font color="cyan">Tristan?</font>

29:23.759 --> 29:24.999
<font color="cyan">TRISTAN!</font>

29:29.199 --> 29:30.399
<font color="cyan">TRISTAN!</font>

29:39.439 --> 29:41.319
<font color="yellow">Here, before you go.</font>

29:42.679 --> 29:44.479
<font color="yellow">In case you get your appetite</font>
<font color="yellow">back later.</font>

29:46.399 --> 29:47.439
<font color="lime">Thank you.</font>

29:48.679 --> 29:51.159
<font color="yellow">Once everyone's calmed down a bit,</font>
<font color="yellow">they'll see.</font>

29:51.159 --> 29:52.319
<font color="yellow">What you did was right.</font>

29:55.679 --> 29:57.279
<font color="lime">What I thought was right.</font>

29:57.279 --> 30:00.719
<font color="yellow">Don't dwell on what's done</font>
<font color="yellow">when there's things need doing.</font>

30:00.719 --> 30:03.439
<font color="yellow">Mrs Calvert's been on the phone,</font>
<font color="yellow">wants someone up there again.</font>

30:03.439 --> 30:07.719
<font color="yellow">It's time to get back in the saddle,</font>
<font color="yellow">sorry, poor choice of words.</font>

30:25.959 --> 30:27.439
<font color="white">Morning.</font>

30:27.439 --> 30:28.679
<font color="white">Look ahead. Look ahead.</font>

30:28.679 --> 30:30.519
<font color="lime">Tristan!</font>

30:30.519 --> 30:31.799
<font color="lime">What're you doing?</font>

30:31.799 --> 30:33.359
<font color="white">Trying to save my skin.</font>

30:35.519 --> 30:37.719
<font color="lime">You spent the money, didn't you?</font>

30:37.719 --> 30:39.479
<font color="white">Don't worry, I have a plan.</font>

30:40.759 --> 30:42.079
<font color="white">Drive. Just drive.</font>

30:50.359 --> 30:53.199
<font color="lime">You know there's still a chance</font>
<font color="lime">your horse might not come in.</font>

30:53.199 --> 30:55.679
<font color="white">Fortes Fortuna iogurtum.</font>

30:55.679 --> 30:58.879
<font color="lime">Fortune favours the yoghurt?</font>

30:58.879 --> 31:01.119
<font color="white">No, the brave.</font>
<font color="white">Fortune favours the brave.</font>

31:01.119 --> 31:02.239
<font color="lime">That's iuvat.</font>

31:02.239 --> 31:03.759
<font color="lime">Fortes Fortuna Iuvat.</font>

31:05.359 --> 31:06.439
<font color="white">Never the less.</font>

31:06.439 --> 31:08.719
<font color="white">You took a gamble on your horse,</font>
<font color="white">I took one on mine.</font>

31:08.719 --> 31:11.039
<font color="white">Either one or both or neither of us</font>
<font color="white">are for the high jump.</font>

31:11.039 --> 31:13.399
<font color="lime">I didn't gamble. </font><font color="white">No. Of course.</font>
<font color="white">Turn of phrase.</font>

31:17.079 --> 31:18.399
<font color="lime">Oh, not again!</font>

31:24.039 --> 31:25.759
<font color="white">Isn't that the lovely Miss Alderson?</font>

31:25.759 --> 31:27.359
<font color="cyan">Good morning to you too, James!</font>

31:28.319 --> 31:29.359
<font color="lime">Hold on.</font>

31:29.359 --> 31:30.399
<font color="lime">Let me back up!</font>

31:40.679 --> 31:43.759
<font color="lime">Sorry, my mind was somewhere else.</font>

31:43.759 --> 31:45.519
<font color="cyan">I'm sure it was.</font>

31:45.519 --> 31:48.359
<font color="lime">You heard?</font>
<font color="cyan">Hugh told me last night.</font>

31:48.359 --> 31:50.399
<font color="cyan">Andante meant the world to him.</font>

31:50.399 --> 31:51.639
<font color="cyan">It sounded awful.</font>

31:51.639 --> 31:53.119
<font color="yellow">He called you a bas...</font>
<font color="cyan">Jenny!</font>

31:54.519 --> 31:56.479
<font color="white">Ah, out of the mouth of babes.</font>

31:58.399 --> 31:59.799
<font color="lime">I had to do it.</font>

31:59.799 --> 32:02.439
<font color="cyan">You don't have to explain</font>
<font color="cyan">yourself to me. It was Hugh's horse.</font>

32:02.439 --> 32:05.799
<font color="lime">No, I know. It's just, you're his,</font>
<font color="lime">his...</font>

32:07.559 --> 32:09.959
<font color="lime">His, err, fiancee?</font>

32:11.279 --> 32:12.839
<font color="cyan">Unless you know something I don't.</font>

32:15.799 --> 32:17.319
<font color="cyan">I best get on.</font>
<font color="cyan">Good luck today.</font>

32:25.039 --> 32:26.359
<font color="white">And what was all that about?</font>

32:27.639 --> 32:29.639
<font color="lime">Hmm?</font>
<font color="white">I saw you.</font>

32:29.639 --> 32:30.959
<font color="white">I saw that look.</font>

32:30.959 --> 32:32.399
<font color="lime">It's nothing.</font>

32:32.399 --> 32:33.719
<font color="white">Now I am intrigued.</font>

32:36.159 --> 32:38.839
<font color="lime">I asked her out.</font>
<font color="white">Oh, James, you didn't.</font>

32:38.839 --> 32:40.479
<font color="lime">Mrs Pumphrey's do.</font>

32:40.479 --> 32:42.159
<font color="lime">Took all night to pluck up</font>
<font color="lime">the courage.</font>

32:42.159 --> 32:43.559
<font color="white">Dutch courage?</font>

32:43.559 --> 32:47.039
<font color="lime">Might as well have been</font>
<font color="lime">Abyssinian for all the good it did.</font>

32:47.039 --> 32:50.439
<font color="lime">I'd just made my play,</font>
<font color="lime">and in walks Hugh.</font>

32:50.439 --> 32:51.839
<font color="white">And then you killed his horse.</font>

32:53.319 --> 32:56.639
<font color="white">It's unorthodox, but I have to say</font>
<font color="white">I admire the gumption.</font>

33:05.199 --> 33:07.199
<font color="cyan">You're sure this isn't putting</font>
<font color="cyan">you out too much?</font>

33:07.199 --> 33:08.519
<font color="yellow">Oh, it's no trouble at all.</font>

33:08.519 --> 33:09.799
<font color="cyan">You're a godsend, we've got</font>

33:09.799 --> 33:12.359
<font color="cyan">a load of hay to bring in and then</font>
<font color="cyan">there's all with Hugh's horse.</font>

33:12.359 --> 33:13.479
<font color="cyan">Right, come here you.</font>

33:15.279 --> 33:17.319
<font color="yellow">How is he? </font><font color="cyan">In pieces.</font>

33:17.319 --> 33:18.799
<font color="cyan">Not that he'd admit it.</font>

33:18.799 --> 33:21.119
<font color="yellow">You'll sweep him up and put him</font>
<font color="yellow">back together again.</font>

33:21.119 --> 33:22.479
<font color="cyan">Isn't that our lot in life?</font>

33:22.479 --> 33:23.839
<font color="yellow">For you more than most.</font>

33:24.879 --> 33:26.359
<font color="yellow">If you ever fancy a natter...</font>

33:28.399 --> 33:29.719
<font color="cyan">There's not much more to say.</font>

33:30.799 --> 33:31.999
<font color="cyan">I best get on.</font>

33:31.999 --> 33:33.239
<font color="cyan">I'll be back before tea.</font>

33:36.119 --> 33:38.279
<font color="yellow">All these need cleaning out.</font>

33:38.279 --> 33:41.239
<font color="yellow">And after that you can feed</font>
<font color="yellow">and exercise them.</font>

33:41.239 --> 33:43.519
<font color="cyan">Can I play with the bunnies?</font>

33:43.519 --> 33:45.719
<font color="cyan">Can I take the dogs</font>
<font color="cyan">for a walk on the green?</font>

33:45.719 --> 33:48.319
<font color="yellow">If you like. But first,</font>
<font color="yellow">I want you to have a look at this.</font>

33:48.319 --> 33:50.519
<font color="cyan">Don't you start with all</font>
<font color="cyan">the books an'all.</font>

33:50.519 --> 33:54.599
<font color="yellow">What should a good vet do for a</font>
<font color="yellow">rabbit with suspected Ivy poisoning?</font>

33:55.959 --> 33:59.159
<font color="cyan">The only rabbits I know</font>
<font color="cyan">they put in pies.</font>

34:02.079 --> 34:04.839
<font color="yellow">Well, Mr Farnon won't have any</font>
<font color="yellow">Tom, Dick or Harry tending</font>

34:04.839 --> 34:07.439
<font color="yellow">to his animals, they need to</font>
<font color="yellow">know their stuff first.</font>

34:18.079 --> 34:19.119
<font color="cyan">Morning Mr Soames.</font>

34:19.359 --> 34:20.399
<font color="yellow">Morning. </font><font color="cyan">Hugh.</font>

34:23.759 --> 34:25.679
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry it's come to this.</font>

34:25.679 --> 34:27.559
<font color="cyan">As am I. Where is he?</font>

34:42.159 --> 34:43.199
<font color="yellow">I should be here.</font>

34:45.119 --> 34:46.438
<font color="yellow">I owe it to him to be here.</font>

35:10.639 --> 35:13.079
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear, oh, dear.</font>

35:13.079 --> 35:16.439
<font color="yellow">Here's trouble,</font>
<font color="yellow">Herriot the Horse Killer.</font>

35:17.479 --> 35:18.519
<font color="lime">What?</font>

35:18.519 --> 35:21.239
<font color="yellow">Word's got around,</font>
<font color="yellow">not many of them good.</font>

35:21.239 --> 35:24.399
<font color="yellow">I thought they'd have you</font>
<font color="yellow">out on your ear by now.</font>

35:24.399 --> 35:26.599
<font color="lime">So, what seems to be</font>
<font color="lime">the problem today?</font>

35:26.599 --> 35:28.079
<font color="yellow">Calf gone daft.</font>

35:29.079 --> 35:31.759
<font color="yellow">But I'd like Mr Siegfried to</font>
<font color="yellow">look it over.</font>

35:34.999 --> 35:37.719
<font color="white">My brother is otherwise engaged.</font>

35:37.719 --> 35:39.559
<font color="white">So it'll be Jim or no-one.</font>

35:47.519 --> 35:49.239
<font color="lime">And how long has he been like this?</font>

35:49.239 --> 35:51.759
<font color="yellow">I first noticed something this</font>
<font color="yellow">morning.</font>

35:51.759 --> 35:52.919
<font color="yellow">Swear he was drunk,</font>

35:52.919 --> 35:55.959
<font color="yellow">the way he's been staggering about</font>
<font color="yellow">and bumping into things.</font>

35:55.959 --> 35:56.999
<font color="yellow">Not right, is it?</font>

35:58.639 --> 35:59.999
<font color="lime">No, Mrs Calvert, it's not.</font>

36:01.679 --> 36:04.679
<font color="lime">OK.</font>

36:06.799 --> 36:07.959
<font color="yellow">Well, what you reckon?</font>

36:22.119 --> 36:23.679
<font color="lime">I just don't know.</font>

36:23.679 --> 36:26.879
<font color="white">The process of veterinary</font>
<font color="white">discovery often takes time.</font>

36:26.879 --> 36:29.359
<font color="yellow">Yeah, just so long as he don't</font>
<font color="yellow">wind up killing him.</font>

36:32.199 --> 36:35.519
<font color="white">Any ideas, Jim?</font>
<font color="white">You're rather losing your audience.</font>

36:35.519 --> 36:39.999
<font color="lime">We've got muscle tremors,</font>
<font color="lime">frothing from the mouth, confusion.</font>

36:39.999 --> 36:41.959
<font color="white">That's me every morning,</font>
<font color="white">Mrs Calvert.</font>

36:41.959 --> 36:44.119
<font color="white">No need to look so worried.</font>

36:44.119 --> 36:47.439
<font color="white">Blimey then, this place has seen</font>
<font color="white">better days, hasn't it?</font>

36:51.599 --> 36:53.079
<font color="lime">Where did this wood come from?</font>

36:53.079 --> 36:54.999
<font color="yellow">Bit of old skirting board.</font>

36:54.999 --> 36:56.439
<font color="yellow">Waste not, want not.</font>

36:56.439 --> 36:57.479
<font color="lime">Look at the paint.</font>

36:58.679 --> 37:00.079
<font color="lime">It's flaking.</font>

37:00.079 --> 37:01.319
<font color="lime">He's been licking it.</font>

37:01.319 --> 37:03.599
<font color="lime">And biting,</font>
<font color="lime">I can see the teeth marks.</font>

37:03.599 --> 37:05.359
<font color="yellow">He's a cow.</font>

37:05.359 --> 37:06.399
<font color="yellow">It's what they do.</font>

37:08.679 --> 37:09.719
<font color="lime">It's lead paint.</font>

37:11.039 --> 37:13.479
<font color="lime">He's got lead poisoning.</font>
<font color="lime">Get this wood out of here.</font>

37:13.479 --> 37:15.799
<font color="yellow">You heard.</font>
<font color="yellow">Jump to it.</font>

37:15.799 --> 37:18.159
<font color="lime">A couple of spoonfuls of Epsom</font>
<font color="lime">salts in her feed,</font>

37:18.159 --> 37:20.319
<font color="lime">and all will be well again.</font>

37:20.319 --> 37:21.959
<font color="lime">I'll be back to</font>
<font color="lime">check in a couple of days.</font>

37:21.959 --> 37:24.399
<font color="yellow">Well, at least someone will be.</font>

37:24.399 --> 37:26.679
<font color="yellow">All the best, horse killer.</font>

37:32.719 --> 37:35.799
<font color="white">You know, everyone will forget</font>
<font color="white">eventually.</font>

37:35.799 --> 37:37.479
<font color="lime">If my diagnosis was correct.</font>

37:38.879 --> 37:39.919
<font color="lime">If it wasn't...</font>

37:41.279 --> 37:42.519
<font color="lime">..I'll be packing my bags.</font>

38:02.359 --> 38:04.159
<font color="white">Moment of truth, James.</font>

38:04.159 --> 38:05.199
<font color="white">Wish me luck.</font>

38:07.759 --> 38:11.999
<font color="white">Maggie, the sword of Damocles</font>
<font color="white">dangles by a mere thread.</font>

38:11.999 --> 38:13.719
<font color="white">Please tell me who won the race.</font>

38:18.959 --> 38:20.119
<font color="yellow">Finlay Bay came in.</font>

38:21.639 --> 38:23.839
<font color="white">Thank goodness.</font>
<font color="white">Maggie, I could kiss you.</font>

38:23.839 --> 38:26.159
<font color="yellow">Well, not without my say so.</font>
<font color="white">Sorry.</font>

38:27.799 --> 38:29.639
<font color="yellow">Go on, then.</font>
<font color="white">What? Really?</font>

38:37.199 --> 38:39.879
<font color="yellow">Is this him, then?</font>
<font color="yellow">The horse killer?</font>

38:41.879 --> 38:43.559
<font color="yellow">I reckon I owe you a pint.</font>

38:43.559 --> 38:46.519
<font color="yellow">Saved me paying out to half</font>
<font color="yellow">the county by offing that horse.</font>

38:50.119 --> 38:52.479
<font color="yellow">I think we might have a budding</font>
<font color="yellow">vet on our hands.</font>

38:53.719 --> 38:56.279
<font color="cyan">It's just good to see her so happy.</font>
<font color="lime">Come on, Jess...</font>

38:58.279 --> 39:01.399
<font color="yellow">You know, she parroted your old</font>
<font color="yellow">man yesterday.</font>

39:01.399 --> 39:03.239
<font color="yellow">She said to me, bold as brass,</font>

39:03.239 --> 39:05.999
<font color="yellow">'we were born to the land to work</font>
<font color="yellow">the land'.</font>

39:09.439 --> 39:11.199
<font color="cyan">That won't me</font>
<font color="cyan">old man she were parroting.</font>

39:12.559 --> 39:13.599
<font color="cyan">It was me mother.</font>

39:18.519 --> 39:20.319
<font color="cyan">I'm always worried I'm</font>
<font color="cyan">letting her down.</font>

39:23.199 --> 39:25.119
<font color="yellow">You're doing a great job.</font>

39:26.199 --> 39:27.599
<font color="yellow">Your mother would be proud.</font>

39:29.079 --> 39:30.719
<font color="cyan">Don't, you'll start me off.</font>

39:33.079 --> 39:34.319
<font color="yellow">Jenny's getting older.</font>

39:35.359 --> 39:38.279
<font color="yellow">Maybe right now,</font>
<font color="yellow">she needs a big sister.</font>

39:38.279 --> 39:39.759
<font color="yellow">More than she needs a mother.</font>

39:43.039 --> 39:44.199
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

39:44.199 --> 39:45.239
<font color="lime">Fetch!</font>

39:49.759 --> 39:53.039
<font color="cyan">Come on then. Right, let's see</font>
<font color="cyan">if you can beat the dog, Jenny!</font>

40:05.799 --> 40:06.879
<font color="yellow">How were it?</font>

40:23.479 --> 40:24.519
<font color="cyan">James.</font>

40:33.439 --> 40:35.239
<font color="cyan">The postmortem was</font>
<font color="cyan">quite conclusive.</font>

40:38.199 --> 40:39.959
<font color="cyan">Significant torsion of the bowel.</font>

40:48.039 --> 40:50.759
<font color="cyan">There was necrosis, so he'd</font>
<font color="cyan">been in that state for a while.</font>

40:52.159 --> 40:54.399
<font color="cyan">Absolutely nothing you could</font>
<font color="cyan">have done for him,</font>

40:54.399 --> 40:56.039
<font color="cyan">except put him out of his misery.</font>

40:58.239 --> 41:01.559
<font color="lime">And Hugh? He agrees with that?</font>

41:01.559 --> 41:04.759
<font color="lime">I'm not sure either of us will be</font>
<font color="lime">welcome at his stables for a bit.</font>

41:09.919 --> 41:12.239
<font color="cyan">James, your diagnosis,</font>

41:12.239 --> 41:15.839
<font color="cyan">your chosen course of action</font>
<font color="cyan">were both text book.</font>

41:15.839 --> 41:17.279
<font color="lime">Then why don't I feel any better?</font>

41:18.479 --> 41:20.799
<font color="cyan">Because you had to euthanize</font>
<font color="cyan">a beautiful, young animal.</font>

41:22.959 --> 41:24.639
<font color="white">Never doubted you for a second, Jim.</font>

41:24.639 --> 41:26.559
<font color="cyan">There you are! Where is it?</font>

41:26.559 --> 41:28.879
<font color="white">BELL RINGS</font>
<font color="cyan">You've lost the money, haven't you?</font>

41:28.879 --> 41:30.039
<font color="white">See for yourself.</font>

41:36.999 --> 41:38.639
<font color="cyan">I'll be checking</font>
<font color="cyan">it against the ledger.</font>

41:38.639 --> 41:40.479
<font color="cyan">If there's</font>
<font color="cyan">so much of an ha'penny missing...</font>

41:40.479 --> 41:42.119
<font color="white">I'll be flogged and boiled in oil.</font>

41:42.119 --> 41:43.159
<font color="yellow">Mr Farnon.</font>

41:43.279 --> 41:44.479
<font color="yellow">It's for you.</font>

41:49.599 --> 41:50.639
<font color="cyan">General.</font>

41:50.639 --> 41:53.599
<font color="white">Siegfried, I was rather</font>
<font color="white">hoping to see you at the racecourse.</font>

41:53.599 --> 41:55.239
<font color="cyan">I didn't think there was much point.</font>

41:55.239 --> 41:56.919
<font color="cyan">I assume you've spoken to</font>
<font color="cyan">Hugh Hulton?</font>

41:56.919 --> 41:59.119
<font color="white">Yes. Terrible business.</font>
<font color="cyan">Awful.</font>

41:59.119 --> 42:02.039
<font color="white">Well, I thought</font>
<font color="white">you were very impressive yesterday,</font>

42:02.039 --> 42:04.559
<font color="white">and I'd still like to</font>
<font color="white">offer you the role.</font>

42:04.559 --> 42:06.519
<font color="cyan">General, I can't thank you enough.</font>

42:06.519 --> 42:08.079
<font color="cyan">You won't regret it, I assure you.</font>

42:08.079 --> 42:09.399
<font color="white">I said I'd like to.</font>

42:09.399 --> 42:12.999
<font color="white">But I fear that many</font>
<font color="white">of my owners would be very twitchy,</font>

42:12.999 --> 42:16.239
<font color="white">when they know that you're</font>
<font color="white">associated with that Herriot chap.</font>

42:17.239 --> 42:20.119
<font color="cyan">But he did absolutely</font>
<font color="cyan">the right thing.</font>

42:20.119 --> 42:22.679
<font color="cyan">The postmortem couldn't be</font>
<font color="cyan">more clearer. </font><font color="white">Even so.</font>

42:22.759 --> 42:24.959
<font color="white">Killing the pride</font>
<font color="white">and joy of Darrowby.</font>

42:24.959 --> 42:26.479
<font color="white">Hmm? Never a good look.</font>

42:27.919 --> 42:29.799
<font color="white">If you want this job</font>
<font color="white">he'll have to go.</font>

42:29.799 --> 42:30.999
<font color="white">Do we have an understanding?</font>

42:34.759 --> 42:35.919
<font color="cyan">Actually we don't.</font>

42:37.559 --> 42:41.279
<font color="cyan">Yesterday, you agreed the welfare</font>
<font color="cyan">of the animal came first.</font>

42:42.639 --> 42:44.799
<font color="cyan">Today it seems that's not the case.</font>

42:47.879 --> 42:49.919
<font color="cyan">Herriot's the best assistant</font>
<font color="cyan">I've ever had.</font>

42:51.239 --> 42:53.999
<font color="cyan">I won't betray him for anything.</font>

42:53.999 --> 42:58.439
<font color="white">Then, with regret, I'm afraid we</font>
<font color="white">shan't be requiring your services.</font>

43:00.719 --> 43:01.759
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

43:03.519 --> 43:04.599
<font color="cyan">Good evening.</font>

43:05.679 --> 43:06.719
<font color="white">Good evening.</font>

43:23.559 --> 43:25.239
<font color="cyan">I didn't get the job.</font>

43:25.239 --> 43:26.279
<font color="yellow">I heard.</font>

43:28.279 --> 43:30.479
<font color="cyan">I can't lie,</font>
<font color="cyan">it would've been tremendous.</font>

43:32.799 --> 43:33.839
<font color="cyan">Still.</font>

43:35.039 --> 43:38.319
<font color="yellow">You're a good man Siegfried Farnon,</font>

43:38.319 --> 43:40.639
<font color="yellow">no matter how much you</font>
<font color="yellow">try to hide it.</font>

43:40.639 --> 43:42.479
<font color="cyan">Yes, well, keep it to yourself.</font>

43:42.479 --> 43:44.359
<font color="cyan">We don't want people thinking</font>
<font color="cyan">I've gone soft.</font>

43:46.919 --> 43:49.199
<font color="yellow">We've had a few calls.</font>

43:49.199 --> 43:51.519
<font color="yellow">Seems folk would rather you</font>
<font color="yellow">visit than James.</font>

43:54.639 --> 43:56.839
<font color="cyan">Can't imagine it'll be easy for him.</font>

43:56.839 --> 43:58.159
<font color="yellow">They'll come round.</font>

43:59.879 --> 44:01.359
<font color="cyan">Let's see to it, that they do.</font>

44:05.359 --> 44:07.639
<font color="cyan">Tristan, get your bloody feet off</font>
<font color="cyan">the table!</font>

44:07.639 --> 44:09.959
<font color="cyan">Do you think you're in some</font>
<font color="cyan">kind of backroom bordello!?</font>

44:09.959 --> 44:12.199
<font color="white">Chance'd be a fine thing.</font>

44:12.199 --> 44:14.839
<font color="cyan">Fetch me the ledger. I want to go</font>
<font color="cyan">through it with a fine tooth comb.</font>

44:14.839 --> 44:17.119
<font color="cyan">I want every penny accounted for.</font>

44:17.119 --> 44:18.159
<font color="cyan">Jump to it.</font>

44:20.559 --> 44:22.079
<font color="cyan">Now, Herriot, what about you?</font>

44:23.119 --> 44:24.239
<font color="lime">What about me?</font>

44:24.239 --> 44:26.679
<font color="cyan">Well, you've a list as long</font>
<font color="cyan">as my arm to prepare for tomorrow.</font>

44:26.679 --> 44:29.959
<font color="cyan">Mrs Hall's had a whole load of</font>
<font color="cyan">calls, and you're doing all of them.</font>

44:32.119 --> 44:33.839
<font color="lime">Is this some kind of punishment?</font>

44:33.839 --> 44:35.479
<font color="cyan">Quite the opposite.</font>

44:35.479 --> 44:37.199
<font color="cyan">Go on, we've got a practice to run.</font>

44:45.839 --> 44:47.239
<font color="yellow">I'll fetch you a fresh one.</font>

